milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (469) involving teams West Indies & Sri Lanka in ODIs
Roy Dias and Uvais Karnain's 78-run partnership is SL's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 68 between Madugalle and Ranasinghe
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (35) for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
Holding has become the highest wicket-taker in ODIs with 104 wickets, going past Dennis Lillee's 103
